Subject: Need to extend Disk Space in new EPP server (Migrating old EPP Server - QOFOZ33V)
Description: We are migrating old EPP Server - QOFOZ33V to new. But we need to extend the disk space in it. It is taking only approx 250 GB but we want to extend it to 1 TB. Kindly help in extending the disk space.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Requesting more disk space for the VM
What_We_Know__c:
They have an old server and also a new one
They had a low disk space warning in the old server
Solution_Comment__c:
Performed disk extensions for the old server and also for the new one.
Cleared disk space on the Root partition of the old server to resolve the warning message.
